      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The hemolysis index and shear stress distribution are directly relevant quantities of interest for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. These QoIs are established in the literature and regulatory guidance for CPB device assessment."
